{"tid":1640912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母！！！點先制裁到班死黑警！！！","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T11:23:17.000Z","uid":110,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c14e5ef109650ce2b92d81c351c2db623cdac33","tid":1640912,"uid":110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母！！！！<br />\n日日睇住班黑警攬捕 強姦 殺人 棄屍 老屈 打人<br />\n真係好撚唔明白佢地憑咩生存係呢個世界！！！<br />\n到底有冇天理架我屌！黑社會又唔捉 後生就日日捉<br />\n我日日返工就掛住睇新聞 夜晚就睇live 每晚都訓得唔安樂真係好痛苦！點解冇人可以制裁佢地 <br />\n衣家蒙面法之後重撚衰 咩罪名都冇就直接搭鳩你！<br />\n到底我要點做 呢架真係長期消磨緊意志 日日都情緒不穩 6月9號開始冇一日真正笑過！"},{"pid":"eb2107609b029293f0c062942d80d2a2a9682f9c","tid":1640912,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"手足 支持住<br />\n我地要等到宜班黑警被清算<br />\n唔好放棄 !"},{"pid":"1fadc152e31ff2f0bccaa6f51f63554617d7583d","tid":1640912,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2107609b029293f0c062942d80d2a2a9682f9c","tid":1640912,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"手足 支持住<br />\n我地要等到宜班黑警被清算<br />\n唔好放棄 !"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"點清算<br />\n邊個清算<br />\n邊個話有清算"},{"pid":"6a5680c9baf5cc8e580cc7b854080e553577f500","tid":1640912,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"高空奇襲<br />\n黃車擊殺<br />\n佢地最撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1aa8437142b1c5a732d97bbb228ed9b70a3fc","tid":1640912,"uid":110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2107609b029293f0c062942d80d2a2a9682f9c","tid":1640912,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"手足 支持住<br />\n我地要等到宜班黑警被清算<br />\n唔好放棄 !"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"我每日都會諗起天琦封信 不要被仇恨支配 <br />\n但真係太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\"